==不實廣告==
*有些不肖廠商會宣稱或間接暗示產品通過80 PLUS認證，即使產品並無達到80 PLUS之標準。<ref name=Fake80 />
*在80 PLUS官方網站上詳細記載通過80 PLUS之電源供應器與詳細測試內容，可確認個人電源供應器是否通過認證。<ref name=80PlusList>{{Cite web | url = http://www.plugloadsolutions.com/80PlusPowerSupplies.aspx | title = 80 Plus PSU List | publisher = 80 PLUS | accessdate = October 31, 2011 | archive-date = 2012-09-14 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6AfcJlS8S?url=http://www.plugloadsolutions.com/80PlusPowerSupplies.aspx | dead-url = yes }}</ref>
*即使有些廠商以與80 PLUS相似的名稱介紹產品（如 85 PLUS），但其實並無如此的官方規範與標準。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.hardwaresecrets.com/article/941 | title = 85 Plus PSU | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110711161717/http://www.hardwaresecrets.com/article/941 | archivedate = 2011-07-11 | accessdate = 2011-12-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.tomshardware.com/reviews/500w-psu-power-supply,2658-6.html | title = FSP Everest 85 PLUS 500 | accessdate = 2011-12-14 | archive-date = 2012-09-14 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6AfcVNa5p?url=http://www.tomshardware.com/reviews/500w-psu-power-supply,2658-6.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*當代工廠商交貨[[OEM|OEM]]電源供應器給委託廠商時，電源供應器必須再重新被80 PLUS認證一次，即使在代工廠商時已通過認證。<ref name=Fake80>{{cite web |url = http://www.hardwaresecrets.com/article/Power-Supplies-With-Fake-80-Plus-Badges/1054 |title = Power Supplies With Fake 80 Plus Badges |accessdate = 2010-10-08 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110711161931/http://www.hardwaresecrets.com/article/Power-Supplies-With-Fake-80-Plus-Badges/1054 |archivedate = 2011-07-11 }}</ref>

==意義==
[[File:CMPSU-620HX.jpg|缩略图]]
*決定電源供應器轉換效率的關鍵在於能將多少百分比的輸入轉換為輸出，剩下的電力則會轉換成廢熱。例如，一個轉換效率60%的600足瓦電源供應器，在滿載時會消耗600/0.6=1000瓦的電力，剩下的400瓦則會轉換成不必要的熱能。如果該電源供應器轉換效率為80%，則滿載時僅需消耗750瓦的電力，150瓦的電力則轉換成熱能。
*電源供應器在不同負載程度時有不同的轉換效率。一般來說，電源供應器效率最高時在負載程度50%~75%，低負載與滿載時效率較差。老舊的電源供應器轉換效率大多在60%到75%。
*電源供應器必須在負載程度為20%、50%、100%時皆有大於80%轉換效率才能通過80 PLUS認證。然而，一顆通過80 PLUS認證的電源供器在低負載時轉換效率也有可能低於80%。例如，一顆通過80 PLUS認證的520瓦電源供器在輸出60瓦（一般電腦閒置時大概消耗瓦數）時可能只有70%或更少的轉換效率。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.silentpcreview.com/article692-page4.html | title = Corsair HX520W & HX620W Modular power supplies | work = Silent PC Review | author = Mike Chin | date = 17 November 2006 | accessdate = 2011-12-14 | archive-date = 2011-12-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111214082052/http://www.silentpcreview.com/article692-page4.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>因此，挑選一顆在低負載仍有高轉換效率的電源供應器亦為重要。
*高瓦數的電源供應器較容易達到高轉換效率。因此，80 PLUS金牌和白金在低瓦數電源供應器較難見到。
*減少廢熱產生即代表減少噪音，因風扇不需以高轉速帶走廢熱。減少廢熱、散熱需求即是增加電腦耐用度。<ref name="80PLUS">{{cite web | url = http://www.80plus.org | title = The 80 PLUS Program | accessdate = 2011-12-14 | archive-date = 2010-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101025073119/http://80plus.org/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>
*測試環境亦會影響到電源轉換效率，電源供應器在滿載時會因溫度的提升而有較差的轉換效率。即使測試通常在室溫環境進行，但此疑慮仍存在。<ref name="SPCRNewLevels">{{cite web | url = http://www.silentpcreview.com/article814-page1.html | title = 80 Plus expands podium for Bronze, Silver & Gold | author = Mike Chin | work = Silent PC Review | date = 19 March 2008 | accessdate = 2008-04-21 | archive-date = 2012-09-14 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6AfcKXV4Y?url=http://www.silentpcreview.com/article814-page1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*80 PLUS未對極低的負載程度有所規範。舉例來說，待命中的電源供應器也許會有極差的轉換效率，不符合常見之待機消耗1瓦要求（[[一瓦特倡議|一瓦特倡議]]），即使電源供應器通過80 PLUS。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.silentpcreview.com/article813-page4.html | title = Corsair TX650W power supply review | work = Silent PC Review | accessdate = 2011-12-14 | archive-date = 2011-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111225224839/http://www.silentpcreview.com/article813-page4.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.silentpcreview.com/article806-page5.html | title = Enermax Modu82+ 625 Power Supply Review | work = Silent PC Review | accessdate = 2011-12-14 | archive-date = 2011-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111225224900/http://www.silentpcreview.com/article806-page5.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*80 PLUS僅對轉換效率有所規範，無關[[電源供應器|電源供應器]]之保護機制（如過電壓、低電壓、過電流、短路、過溫、過負載等）。因此，一顆通過80 PLUS之電源供應器不代表有完善保護機制。

